Merge branch '2020.06.x'
* 2020.06.x: MIR-994 allow export of publication list with a csl style MIR-998-problems_with_search_entity (#598) MIR-1004 add article number to metadata view and editor (#605) MIR-1006 publications with date issued range generate invalid datacite MIR-1008 NPE in MirSelfRegistrationServlet MIR-1010 Added Blog as a new document type (#622) MIR-1011 Added new required keyword template field MIR-1013 use pica2mods library for enrichment resolver (#615) MIR-1021 remove obsolete code for managed PIDs, is already solved ... (#620) MIR-1022 MIRStrategy does not work right and is not testet (#623) MIR-1023 do not pass Content-Security-Policy-Header from solr MIR-1026 minor spelling and translation correction in data forms special case for rights_reserved and filter for empty fields added creativework type to all rights served text
